{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I understand Polish and Russian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My Italian is very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I speak quite a bit of Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was just practicing it this morning as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went here to [INAUDIBLE], because I wanted to learn from scratch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always English only.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My German was atrocious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I must say in all honesty, I don't make much effort to learn better German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While I really am-- I must say that at first, while every time I lived in Europe and I saw somebody at the age where I knew they were soldiers-- I saw an SS uniform on them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm able to distinguish now and I don't make a blanket cover.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sure there are some good ones-- excuse me-- and in fact, we made friends with a lovely family from Germany, the [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Irvings, ?] who, of course, knew about my past.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I never made it a secret that I'm Jewish and so is Fred.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were ever so nice that one day they drove us to Dachau because I said to Fred, but for the grace of God, here you come with me to look at what you left in '39.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we correspond and I love them dearly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I truly don't feel that I should be bitter for all that happened to every German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can thank you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say again how very grateful I am that I do have this opportunity to tell my story.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
